image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-15537\" src=\"https://cdn.under.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/3_optimized-1.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" srcset=\"https://cdn.under.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/3_optimized-1.jpg 1000w, https://cdn.under.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/3_optimized-1-300x300.jpg 300w, https://cdn.under.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/3_optimized-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https://cdn.under.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/3_optimized-1-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.under.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/3_optimized-1-510x510.jpg 510w, https://cdn.under.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/3_optimized-1-100x100.jpg 100w\" alt=\"tat-tan-tat-ve-doi-giay-huyen-thoai-vans-old-skool-3\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1000\" /><figcaption><em>Vans Ols Skool x Toy Story</em></figcaption></figure>\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img class=\"wp-image-15538\" src=\"https://cdn.under.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/4_optimized.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 920px) 100vw, 920px\" srcset=\"https://cdn.under.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/4_optimized.jpg 920w, https://cdn.under.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/4_optimized-300x300.jpg 300w, https://cdn.under.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/4_optimized-150x150.jpg 150w, https://cdn.under.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/4_optimized-768x768.jpg 768w, https://cdn.under.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/4_optimized-510x510.jpg 510w, https://cdn.under.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/4_optimized-100x100.jpg 100w\" alt=\"tat-tan-tat-ve-doi-giay-huyen-thoai-vans-old-skool-4\" width=\"920\" height=\"920\" /><figcaption><em>Vans Old Skool x Peanuts</em></figcaption></figure>\r\n<h2 class=\"has-large-font-size\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Điều gì làm nên thành công của Vans Old Skool?</strong></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">“Thời trang – Thời thượng và Không bao giờ lỗi mốt” là những cụm từ mà các sneakerholic thường dùng để miêu tả mỗi khi nhắc đến cái tên Vans Old Skool. Ngày nay, các thương hiệu giày xuất hiện ngày